s=\"lucide lucide-phone h-3.5 w-3.5 text-brand-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg> +1 239-746-8728</a><a href=\"mailto:info.midwestshipment@gmail.com\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-3.5 w-3.5 text-brand-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg> info.midwestshipment@gmail.com</a><span class=\"hidden items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 sm:inline-flex\">Office hours: Mon - Fri 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 justify-end\"><div class=\"language-switcher shrink-0 relative\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 max-w-[12rem] items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[0.75rem] font-bold text-brand-500 shadow-sm transition hover:border-brand-500 hover:text-brand-600\"><span class=\"language-switcher__icon\">🌐</span><span class=\"max-w-full overflow-hidden text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap\">🇺🇸 English</span><span class=\"text-xs\">▼</span></button><div id=\"google_translate_element\" class=\"hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><p class=\"sr-only\">Powered by Google Translate</p></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white transition hover:bg-brand-400\" href=\"/admin/dashboard\">Admin Portal</a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-4 bg-white\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-500 p-2 shadow-sm shadow-brand-500/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package w-5 h-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-900\">Midwest</div><div class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-500\">Shipment Company</div></div></a><div class=\"hidden flex-1 items-center justify-center md:flex\"><nav class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6\"><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/track\">Track Parcel</a></nav></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-900 transition hover:border-brand-400 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/track\">Track Package</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white transition hover:bg-brand-400\" href=\"/contact\">Get Quote</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-3 text-white transition hover:bg-white/10 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center mb-16\"><h1 class=\"text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\">Comprehensive Logistics Services</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">From air freight to secure diplomatic handling, we deliver end-to-end logistics with visible control, dependable coordination, and polished execution.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 transition hover:bg-brand-400\" href=\"/contact\">Get a Quote <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/track\">Track a Shipment</a></div></div></section><section class=\"px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl rounded-[2rem] bg-white/95 p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 sm:p-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-brand-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Why Choose Our Services</p><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl mb-6\">A polished logistics experience from planning to delivery.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 leading-8 mb-8\">Every shipment is managed with a unified approach — rapid coordination, clean communication, and real-time visibility. Whether you need a single leg or a fully integrated logistics program, we build the path around your cargo and timeline.</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-brand-600 shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-slate-700\">Real-time tracking and proactive communication</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-brand-600 shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-slate-700\">Custom handling for fragile and high-value freight</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-brand-600 shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-slate-700\">Cross-border support for smooth customs movement</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-brand-600 shrink-0 mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-slate-700\">Dedicated coordination for urgent and secure cargo</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><p class=\"text-brand-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Our Services</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-6\">Built for air, sea, road, secure, and storage logistics</h2><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Each service is designed to support your cargo with clear communication, secure handling, and tailored dispatch support.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service1.jpg\" alt=\"Air Freight\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Air Freight</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">IATA-endorsed air forwarding for urgent, cross-border shipments with high visibility.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service2.jpg\" alt=\"Sea/Ocean Freight\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Sea/Ocean Freight</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">FCL, LCL, and door-to-door ocean transport backed by professional port handling.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service3.jpg\" alt=\"Road Transportation\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Road Transportation</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">National and regional transport with reliable last-mile delivery coverage.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service4.jpg\" alt=\"Diplomatic Logistics\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Diplomatic Logistics</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">Secure and discreet handling for sensitive materials, documents, and diplomatic cargo.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service5.jpg\" alt=\"Warehousing\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Warehousing</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">Flexible storage solutions with real-time inventory visibility and secure staging.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl h-40\"><img src=\"/images/services/service6.jpg\" alt=\"Packaging &amp; Storage\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Packaging &amp; Storage</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-7 mb-6\">Protective packaging, consolidation, and cargo insurance for every shipment type.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300\" href=\"/contact\">Learn More <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-slate-900/50 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-brand-700 px-8 py-12 text-white\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold\">Need a tailored logistics solution?</h2><p class=\"text-brand-100 text-lg mt-2\">Let&#x27;s build the right plan for your cargo.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-600 shadow-lg transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/contact\">Request a Quote</a></div></div></div></section></main><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-24 pt-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-400\">Trusted by international partners</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl\">Customer testimonials from premium logistics clients</h2></div><div class=\"swiper space-y-8 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\"><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/85 p-10 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-